Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In the year 845, the Colossal Titan\Nand the Armored Titan suddenly appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.70,0:00:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and destroyed one of humanity's walls--\Nand everyday life with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, finally freed\Nfrom their century-long hunger,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the Titans overran humankind once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity abandoned Wall Maria,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,lost 20% of its population\Nand one-third of its territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and was forced to retreat behind Wall Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unknown are the names{\i0}\N{\i1}of the flowers that have been trampled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.66,0:01:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Birds have fallen to the earth{\i0}\N{\i1}and long for the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prayers won't solve anything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Only the will to fight{\i0}\N{\i1}can change the here and now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O pigs who laugh at the resolve{\i0}\N{\i1}to walk over corpses to move forward{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Livestock complacency? False prosperity?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Give us the freedom of dying,{\i0}\N{\i1}starving wolves!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The humiliation of being caged{\i0}\N{\i1}is what triggers us to fight back{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We hunters slaughter prey{\i0}\N{\i1}beyond the castle walls,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.95,0:01:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}consumed with surging bloodlust,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:02:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as our crimson bows and arrows{\i0}\N{\i1}pierce scarlet holes into the twilight{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.37,0:02:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Night of the Closing Ceremony"\N"Humanity's Comeback, Part 2"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Year 850"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Two years after joining the Cadets"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick up the pace! Run, you lead-footed laggards!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem, Arlelt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dragging your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Too heavy for you?!\NMaybe you'd prefer I let you drop your gear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If this were a real mission,\Nyou'd be Titan food by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.16,0:03:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna fail out at this rate!\NWe're being graded today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll get points marked off too if you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then make the grade without\Ngetting found out! Before I change my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiner Braun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stalwart in both mind and body,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and well-respected by his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to be a burden! Even if it costs me my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin Arlelt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Although lacking in physical strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,his aptitude in the classroom is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie Leonhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Her slice attacks are absolutely flawless,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but her reclusive tendencies make her\Na poor fit for coordinated efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Bertholdt Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He possesses remarkable potential,\Nbut lacks aggressiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean Kirschtein.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Top-class omni-directional mobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But his volatile personality\Ntends to cause friction with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't slice as good as those two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to find the Titans before them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If {\i1}anyone {\i0}gets into the Military Police...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...it'll be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the help, Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Following you was a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.95,0:04:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha Braus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She has unconventionally good intuition,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.79,0:04:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but also demonstrates poor teamwork as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Conny Springer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He excels at executing quick turns,\Nbut is also a bit dim-witted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Shallower than Mikasa again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa Ackermann.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely proficient in every area.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's apt to say she's an unmatched,\Nunprecedented genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no real specialties,\Nbut he's improved his grades
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with his unparalleled effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.58,0:05:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And he possesses twice\Nthe sense of purpose than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm not good at holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn to be the rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get this training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would soldiers fight other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Only an idiot would take on a target barehanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's irresponsible thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times we can't run away,\Nno matter how bad the situation is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.83,0:06:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what the enemy is,\Nwe have to be ready for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it means\Nusing cannons or combat techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that's the responsibility of a strong soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, look there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's slacking off without\Nthe commandant noticing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Eren. That slouch needs a talking-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's teach her how a soldier's {\i1}supposed {\i0}to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not fond of the commandant's head-butts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't wanna end up any shorter,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,think back to when you first came here\Nand start taking things seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you being so rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.41,0:07:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, she's mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she looked scary enough as it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's nothing compared to when she's pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Get started, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the drill, right, Annie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She kicked my leg?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No! The drill's not over until you take the dagger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Annie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to do this a certain way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's {\i1}your {\i0}turn to attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No... I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Reiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.62,0:08:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you wanted to teach her\Nabout a soldier's responsibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sometimes a soldier {\i1}can't {\i0}back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is one of those times!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.66,0:08:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an amazing technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you learn it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--Your {\i1}dad {\i0}came up with that move?\N--What does it matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point to any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this training?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We aren't graded on our hand-to-hand combat skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Most people brush it off, like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because only the top ten cadets\Nare allowed to join the Military Police
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and serve in the interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones who take it seriously\Nare naïve idiots like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...or just ordinary idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! The commandant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, in this world,\Nthe better you are at fighting Titans
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the further you can get from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you think this farce came about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... That's a good question!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe because it's human nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I refuse to be stupid enough
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to play "Soldier" in this inane world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're not much of a warrior at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so caught up in getting stronger\Nthat I never realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a clear contradiction...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're honing their Titan-killing skills
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,just to get {\i1}away {\i0}from the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Before Wall Maria fell, only the Scouts\Nneeded omni-directional mobility,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're a small regiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.25,0:10:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,--That put ODM expertise at risk...\N--Give it a strong blast for just a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,--...so this was a way to prevent its decline.\N--Relying on inertia will save you gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe not {\i1}everyone {\i0}can pull it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...but there's no harm in knowing about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,if you wanna join the Military Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'd love to get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.00,0:10:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Working near the king...\NThere's no greater honor than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit talkin' like a goody-two-shoes\Nand say what you {\i1}really {\i0}think!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna join the Military Police
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.66,0:10:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause it means a safe, comfy life in the interior!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I really do want to--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.41,0:11:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's comfy in the interior?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Until five years ago, {\i1}this {\i0}used to be the interior too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your point, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean. You don't need to go to the interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say your head is nice\Nand spacious enough as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.00,0:11:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Honing your Titan-killing skills\Nto get {\i1}away {\i0}from the Titans...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that seem like a weird system to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You only say that {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}want {\i0}that stupid system\Nto stay in place, for my sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You piece of scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! This is the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren! Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.54,0:11:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--Screw you!\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! You're gonna rip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't give a damn about your clothes! I'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He always has to take his feelings out on others...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But not this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to use that move\Nto take control of the situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A combat technique I learned the hard way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,while {\i1}you {\i0}were screwing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A carefree, capricious life\Nis your idea of the real world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.08,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And you honestly call yourself a soldier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a loud sound just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Would anyone care to explain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--It was Sasha. She passed gas.\N--Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You {\i0}again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.58,0:13:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn some decency, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,218 cadets went on to reach graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Give your hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You have three options\Nafter you graduate from the Cadets today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Garrison Regiment,\Nwhich reinforces the walls and protects each city!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The Scout Regiment, which risks life and limb
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.83,0:13:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,to venture into Titan territory outside the walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Military Police Regiment,\Nwhich serves under the king
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,by policing the people and preserving order!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the only ones\Nallowed to join the Military Police
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,are the top ten cadets who were previously named!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We've finally made it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's {\i1}our {\i0}turn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to devour the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm gonna be in the Military Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No more worrying about food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd I get ranked under Eren?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously not gonna join\Nthe Military Police Regiment, Eren?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.45,0:14:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after you got into the top ten and all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind was set from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't train all this time to live in the interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it to fight the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't beat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how many tens of thousands\Nof people have been eaten so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer was clear\Nafter we lost 20% of our population.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity {\i1}can't {\i0}beat the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna give up\Nbecause you think we can't win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--Well...\N--Yes, humanity{\i1} has {\i0}lost so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because we were clueless about the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.50,0:15:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Material warfare is useless against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost, but the information we gained\Nin battle will lead to further hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we just going to throw away\Nall the advances in fighting techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that cost us tens of thousands of lives\Nso we can be Titan fodder?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to drive out every last Titan
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and leave these cramped walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity hasn't {\i1}truly {\i0}been defeated yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wanna go outside the walls, be my guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm {\i0}gonna join the Military Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren. That stuff about your dream just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I borrowed those ideas of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,about going outside instead of staying inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to join the Scout Regiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious, Armin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the top in classroom studies!\NYou should put that to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}won't {\i0}be a burden. Even if it costs me my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join the Scouts too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You graduated top of the class!\NYou should join the Military Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If you join the Military Police, then I will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you join the Garrison Regiment, then I will too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you'll die an early death unless I'm around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose any more of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here! The main unit of the Scout Regiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Erwin! Give those Titans a real thrashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's Captain Levi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They say he's as mighty as an entire brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Talk about annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is nothing like five years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,People actually feel hopeful about the Scout members!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, everyone's cheered up since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.41,0:18:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's happened in five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They've upgraded the mounted cannons too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt the Colossal Titan will show up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a load of crap, you idiotic couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What? {\i1}Us{\i0}, a married couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting ahead of yourself, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hannes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Heard you graduated yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you brats have really matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Mr. Hannes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You used to be a drunk, but now\Nyou're chief of the Corps of Engineers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't save your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.29,0:18:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not ignorant anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't let another tragedy like that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}will {\i0}defeat the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I should be happy\Nthat you've grown up or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go dyin', now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.54,0:19:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're joining the Scouts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Conny! You were so set on the Military Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like your speech yesterday won him over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.91,0:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided it on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.41,0:19:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.87,0:19:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thomas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.37,0:19:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.16,0:19:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought some meat from the officers' storehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha! Do you {\i1}want {\i0}to end up\Nin solitary confinement?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You really {\i1}are {\i0}crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So much it's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We can all share it later...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All sliced up, and between some bread...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:20:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,--Go put it back!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,After we lost all that land,\Nmeat's become really valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We can just raise more cattle and sheep\Nonce we retake our land!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have some of the meat too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me too! Save me some!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have some too, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you just standing there, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get found out if we don't get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch isn't for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.58,0:20:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years have passed since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.66,0:20:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity is finally regaining its dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We can win!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanity's fight back...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:20:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...is just beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.16,0:21:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Samuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Samuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.66,0:21:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.83,0:21:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's happening again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans are going to get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to drive out...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...every last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Every... last one...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.08,0:22:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mounted Cannon Maintenance Squad 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The target is the Colossal Titan dead ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.79,0:22:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance! {\i1}Don't {\i0}let it get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been five years since we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:23:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your dreams are where your heart is{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.95,0:23:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're more fragile than life itself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.20,0:23:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Over and over you cast them aside,{\i0}\N{\i1}only to find more{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, rest in peace{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pounding impulses defile the things we wish for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.87,0:23:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the more we forget{\i0}\N{\i1}the more we remember again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In this beautiful, cruel world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.12,0:23:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}all I can do is ask why we're still alive{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.29,0:23:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, with our strength--and our weakness--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:24:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what are we going to protect if there's no sense{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.66,0:24:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to anything anymore?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.91,0:24:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell opens its mouth once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.41,0:24:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Titans devour the soldiers\Nbefore they can even catch their breaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.91,0:24:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Amid this, Eren saves Armin\Nfrom the brink of death, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.75,0:24:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"First Battle"\N"The Struggle for Trost, Part 1"
